# Ideas

A person can have a favorite station (and direction) and/or lines

When is the next train? The one after? Uptown? Downtown? The next C? The next B?

Parse the alerts ; night time, weekend, non-planned work alerts
--> some alerts may just be benign and there for a long time; maybe like a mailbox concept?

Cache a running history of train times to see how trains are running relative to their scheduled time, how far apart they are

Text a summary each morning around commute time

